claim: William Shatner played T. J. Hooker in the show T. J. Hooker.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Shatner also played the eponymous veteran police sergeant in T. J. Hooker  (  1982 -- 86  )  and hosted the reality-based television series , Rescue 911  (  1989 -- 96  )  , which won a People 's Choice Award for the Favorite New TV Dramatic Series .
